\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb210\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs28\b1\i0 General Principles}
\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Frontiers upholds strict quality standards for manuscripts and the peer-review process through clear criteria and dedicated teams. Manuscripts that pass these criteria are accepted, those that do not pass the criteria are rejected. Frontiers does not reject manuscripts based on their perceived potential impact, nor does it set a rejection rate \endash  formal or informal. Instead, we judge the value and validity of presented work through rigorous quality checks and empower our Editorial Boards to take charge of content decisions. Handling Editors and reviewers can recommend rejection at any time; Editors make acceptance decisions; and Chief Editors make acceptance and rejection decisions. Frontiers\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92 dedicated in-house Research Integrity Team performs pre- and post-review quality screens and can reject articles that do not meet\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.frontiersin.org/about/review-system#AcceptanceCriteria"}{\fldrslt\f1\fs24\b0\i0\ul\ulc0\cf4 acceptance criteria}}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0 . This model ensures rigorous peer review, rapid decisions and the publication of high-quality research.}
\par\pard\plain \sa60\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs20\b1\i0 What is expected of everyone involved?}
\par\pard\plain \li540\fi-270\sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch \ls1\ilvl0{\listtext	\f2\fs24\b1\i0 \uc0\u8226 	}{\f2\fs24\b1\i0 Authors}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \~must submit a manuscript that has significant scholarly value and falls within the scope of the journal. They must comply with all editorial and ethical policies and take all reviewer and editor comments into consideration.}
\par\plain \ilvl0{\listtext	\f2\fs24\b1\i0 \uc0\u8226 	}{\f2\fs24\b1\i0 Reviewers}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \~are subject experts and evaluate manuscripts by using the quality assessment tool and designated review questionnaire that prioritize scientific quality, rigor and validity. They evaluate the methodology of a study for solidity and rigor, ensure the research provides valid conclusions, and is supported by sufficient data.}
\par\plain \ilvl0{\listtext	\f2\fs24\b1\i0 \uc0\u8226 	}{\f2\fs24\b1\i0 Editors}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \~are subject experts and assess the peer-review process and manuscripts meticulously. They only endorse publication if the reviewers validate the contents of a manuscript.}
\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Chief Editors, handling Editors, reviewers and authors are guided and supported by the\~}{\f3\fs24\b0\i1 Frontiers Peer Review Team}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0 , a dedicated team that upholds and ensures high quality standards for manuscripts and the peer review itself, certifying the quality, scientific rigour and validity of research articles and promoting collaboration among authors, reviewers and editors.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 If an editor, reviewer or author is in doubt on how to proceed during the peer-review process, the Frontiers Peer Review Team is the main point of contact for guidance, with two specialized sub-teams: the Research Integrity Team and the Editorial Review Operations Team.}
