\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b1\i0 Conflicts of Interest}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Frontiers is committed to upholding the highest standards of\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.frontiersin.org/about/review-system#PublicationEthics"}{\fldrslt\f1\fs24\b0\i0\ul\ulc0\cf4 publication ethics}}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \~and takes publication malpractice and conflicts of interest very seriously (see our\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "http://www.frontiersin.org/WebTerms.aspx"}{\fldrslt\f1\fs24\b0\i0\ul\ulc0\cf4 Author Conditions}}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0 ). Personal, financial and professional affiliations or relationships can be perceived as conflicts of interest. All authors and all members of Frontiers\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92 Editorial Boards are required to disclose any actual and potential conflicts of interest at submission or upon accepting an editorial or review assignment.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 The Frontiers review system is designed to guarantee transparent and objective editorial and review process, and because handling Editor and reviewers' names are made public upon the publication of articles, conflicts of interest will be openly apparent.}
\par\pard\plain \sa60\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs20\b1\i0 Authors}
\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 As an author, disclosure of any potential\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.frontiersin.org/about/review-system#COI"}{\fldrslt\f1\fs24\b0\i0\ul\ulc0\cf4 conflict of interest}}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \~should be done during the submission process. Consider the following questions and make sure you disclose any positive answers. If you failed to disclose any of the potential\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.frontiersin.org/about/review-system#COI"}{\fldrslt\f1\fs24\b0\i0\ul\ulc0\cf4 conflict of interest}}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \~below during submission, please contact the Frontiers Editorial Office with the details as soon as possible.}
\par\pard\plain \li540\fi-270\sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch \ls15\ilvl0{\listtext	\f1\fs24\b0\i0 1.	}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Did you or your institution at any time receive payment or services from a third party for any aspect of the submitted work?}
\par\plain \ilvl0{\listtext	\f1\fs24\b0\i0 2.	}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Do you have financial relationships with entities that could be perceived to influence, or that give the appearance of potentially influencing, what you wrote in the submitted work?}
\par\plain \ilvl0{\listtext	\f1\fs24\b0\i0 3.	}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Do you have any patents and copyrights, whether pending, issued, licensed and/or receiving royalties related to the research?}
