\par\pard\plain \sa60\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs20\b1\i0 Associate, Topic and Review Editors}
\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Associate Editors, Review Editors and external reviewers are requested to fill a questionnaire before taking on an assignment to disclose any potential conflicts of interest. Research Topic Editors are also asked to complete the questionnaire upon assignment to a manuscript under their Research Topic. If you can answer yes to any of the questions below, Frontiers considers this to be a potential conflict of interest. Such potential conflicts might be between the editor and authors, the reviewers and authors, or the reviewers and editors. Editors are recommended to invite independent reviewers from a broad range of institutional and geographic locations to promote diversity of thought and to ensure an objective and fair peer review process.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 If you have any doubt about whether a relationship or an interest qualifies as a conflict of interest, it is always better to disclose this potential conflict such that editors and the Frontiers Editorial Office can determine whether it necessitates disclosure on the article, or whether an alternate reviewer or editor should be assigned.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Editors must report actual or potential conflicts of interest to the journal's Editorial Office. Reviewers must report actual or potential conflicts of interest both to the journal's Editorial Office and the editor handling the manuscript.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 In case of doubt, please contact your\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.frontiersin.org/about/contact"}{\fldrslt\f1\fs24\b0\i0\ul\ulc0\cf4 Journal's office}}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \~by email, or the main Frontiers Editorial Office at\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "mailto:editorial.office@frontiersin.org"}{\fldrslt\f1\fs24\b0\i0\ul\ulc0\cf4 editorial.office@frontiersin.org}}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0 . You should provide the details of the situation and the potential conflict(s) that you would like to report.}
